Class HypermedeaArtifact

  • java.lang.Object
    • cartago.Artifact
      • org.hypermedea.HypermedeaArtifact
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkedDataArtifact, OntologyArtifact, ThingArtifact
    public abstract class HypermedeaArtifact
extends cartago.Artifact
    Abstract class for all Hypermedea artifacts, holding a reference to objects with restricted access, e.g. a Linked Data crawler.
